summary: I had a dream last night that we were shown Mewtwo's new form for Sword and Shield.  Imagine if Mewtwo Y still had a tail but...
body:
I had a dream last night that we were shown Mewtwo’s new form for Sword and Shield. Imagine if Mewtwo Y still had a tail but that tail pointed forward between its legs and that tail had been bitten by Slowbro’s Shelder, and that ring around its head turns into a weird cork screw hair thing, and the eyes are similar in shape to Slowbro but have Mewtwo Y eyes

People did not react well to it, but I shouted FUSIONS! then everyone else rioted around gf’s building
